I decided to squeeze in a last minute Dollar Tree Christmas DIY today using parking cones and tinsel. I spray painted my cones black and then I’m hot gluing the tinsel around the cone. I did go back in and fill with some extra tinsel and for the 2nd one I actually used 1 and a half strands of tinsel instead of 1. The final step was to hot glue these on to the bottom of my every day planters. I’m putting mine out on my porch steps but it was entirely too windy today but here’s what they look like inside!
